com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface RedhatLinuxLocalUser

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, LinuxLocalUser, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, User
All Known Implementing Classes:
RedhatLinuxLocalUserImpl
public interface RedhatLinuxLocalUser
extends LinuxLocalUser

A representation of the model object 'Redhat Linux Local User'.

The following features are supported:

  • Account Disable After Days
  • Account Disable Date
  • Days Before Password May Change
  • Last Password Change
  • Password Expire After Days
  • Password Expire Warning Days
  • User Sid

See Also:
OsPackage.getRedhatLinuxLocalUser()
